      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is the first news article about my 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1002/smll.202000746&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Small publication&lt;/a&gt; which was published online on 22nd June 2020.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check out the news article 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.myscience.ch/en/news/2020/tiny_fish_under_a_giant_camera-2020-unibas&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;in &lt;strong&gt;English&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, 
